	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi! I am lvl 24 pally playing on Cazic Thule. Right now i am camping AC in SK. My 2H slashing weapon is a 2H Practice Sword, dmg 19 dly 47, procs Shield Of Thistles, does 43-45 dmg max a swing. This is a fairly ok weapon, slow, but still. My 1H Slash is a Fine Steel Scimitar, dmg 5 dly 24. This weapon was fine in the teens, but doing only 11-12 dmg a hit, makes it useless fighting yellow Aviac Harriers, and in a group, I impress no one. I have about 200 PP in bank, what weapon could I hope to buy, or what weapon should I have according to my lvl and mob that i am fighting? Minotaur Battle Axe or Silvery War Axe would be a great improvement i think, but a Short Sword Of The Ykesha, 8-24, would be much better of course. I would highly appreciate any tips for my 1H weapon situation. Best Regards, Pulk Steelswinger on Cazic Thule<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
